  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个简单的时序图，展示两个系统之间的基础交互。场景是系统A先向系统B发送问候，然后B回复一个确认。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "A",
        "B",
        "Hello消息",
        "World回复"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，两个参与者A和B。关于消息方向：A到B的\"Hello\"是普通同步调用还是异步？还有B返回的\"World\"，需要虚线表示返回吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "A-B",
        "B--A",
        "消息类型"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "\"Hello\"是普通请求，用实线箭头。\"World\"是响应，用虚线箭头回去。这是典型的请求-响应模式。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "实线箭头",
        "虚线箭头",
        "请求-响应模式"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先搭建框架：创建参与者A和B，然后画A指向B的实线标注Hello，再画B指向A的虚线标注World。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "participant A",
        "participant B",
        "A-B: Hello",
        "B--A: World"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "等等，B返回的虚线箭头方向确认一下——是从B指向A对吧？不是A自己绕回来。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "B--A",
        "箭头方向"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认，B--A，虚线从B的生命线回到A，标注World。方向正确。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "B--A: World"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "内容很简洁了。不过我在想，参与者名称保持A和B就可以，不需要改成具体系统名，这样通用性更好。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "A",
        "B",
        "命名策略"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "完成。最终结构：参与者A、参与者B，A发送Hello给B（实线），B回复World给A（虚线）。图示已生成。",
      "elements_involved": [
